Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.57,0:02:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是叫得太親暱了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.73,0:02:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.64,0:02:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關羽最近也還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.26,0:02:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒和呂蒙一起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.34,0:03:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說有點不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.67,0:03:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是感冒了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙感冒？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.75,0:03:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.79,0:03:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.71,0:03:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過呂蒙的話 應該不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.21,0:03:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.48,0:03:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與在海邊相遇那次比起來 就好像換了一個人似的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七話 始如處女
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.79,0:03:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 呂蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.34,0:03:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得你過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.07,0:03:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.18,0:03:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 蒙蒙可是特地來找我玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.71,0:03:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起出去也沒什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要罰你打掃衛生 還不明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.27,0:03:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個笨丫頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.11,0:03:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經懂了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.71,0:03:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經充分地十分地發自內心地在反省…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.61,0:03:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？為什麼反省來著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.69,0:03:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見到惇惇 竟然沒把他帶回家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:04:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.69,0:04:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會好好幹的 請讓我盡全力來把它們擦得亮晶晶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.67,0:04:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹完這個後 給院子灑水的活也拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了…瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.15,0:04:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 蒙蒙抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.05,0:04:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 呂蒙小姐過來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.30,0:04:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.68,0:04:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼 伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.17,0:04:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.76,0:04:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 伯符 快離開
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 伯符姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥他看起來很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.62,0:04:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.28,0:04:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公瑾 振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:04:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呂布小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.72,0:04:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真開心啊 劉備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.22,0:05:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.83,0:05:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劉備 再抓緊些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.48,0:05:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.06,0:05:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好涼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉轉過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呂布小姐 好癢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.54,0:05:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不是因為你像小孩子一樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.78,0:05:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擺出一副可怕的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.62,0:06:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫉妒我和劉備的關係了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.24,0:06:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.98,0:06:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙 目的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.18,0:06:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.15,0:06:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呂布奉先 我在叫你離開玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要如此激動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.75,0:06:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.46,0:06:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.40,0:06:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請適可而止吧 你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了保護你才過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.95,0:07:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和關姐在一起的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既難受 又丟人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.71,0:07:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劉備
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧 呂布小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.25,0:07:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.68,0:07:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙又和前任女友死灰復燃了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.26,0:07:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.37,0:07:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的？那現任女友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.69,0:07:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能和她說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.61,0:07:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣保持現狀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.34,0:07:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:07:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個現任女友趕快察覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行 那孩子很遲鈍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛是盲目的 動了真心可就輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.89,0:08:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 真是笨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.28,0:08:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許我說的有點過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.03,0:08:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細想想的話 關姐為了保護我一直都在…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 要進這裡玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很害怕恐怖的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.87,0:08:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人一起進去的話就不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說 你討厭和我一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.87,0:08:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.41,0:09:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要掉了 要掉下去了 呂布小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.58,0:09:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.57,0:09:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕 我果然還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.58,0:09:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事 有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.56,0:09:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.85,0:09:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那就不要離開我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.25,0:09:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.57,0:09:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.98,0:09:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出口在哪裡啊？呂布小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.34,0:09:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呂布小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.82,0:09:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.87,0:09:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不行哦 不好好抓緊我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:09:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呂布小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發信號
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.87,0:10:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德的書…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去遊樂園吧？用不著帶上書吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.69,0:10:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於自己最喜歡的書 難道不想讓它寸步不離己身嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.89,0:11:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呂…呂布小姐 冷不丁地你做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.76,0:11:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呂布小姐 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無需擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.95,0:11:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呂布小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.79,0:11:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是要做些很爽的事情而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.20,0:11:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把呂布奉先帶過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.76,0:11:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.18,0:11:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=======================================12：00
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.89,0:12:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.69,0:12:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劉備玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.43,0:12:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經是我的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:13:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呂布想要接觸左慈 這是很自然的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我卻沒有考慮到這種可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.78,0:13:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是沒有考慮到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.85,0:13:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是根本不想去考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.19,0:13:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.43,0:13:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄…玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 玄德 是我不對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.38,0:14:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.38,0:14:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會呢 關姐沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.44,0:14:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呂布怎麼不在？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說有急事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.60,0:14:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.82,0:14:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德 給你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.16,0:14:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關姐 莫非你哭了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.06,0:14:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是本好書
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果感動到落淚的話 這本書就送給關姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.95,0:14:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經看膩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.69,0:14:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關姐 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.67,0:14:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分感謝 期待您的再次使用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.93,0:14:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呂…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝個樣子給呂蒙看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.73,0:15:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和前任女友死灰復燃了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.11,0:15:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:15:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.14,0:16:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在陣痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.96,0:16:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所要尋找的人 在東南方向距此地不遠處
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.44,0:16:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是那時的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.75,0:16:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 這下就都搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才該道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲謀…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公瑾哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青春啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.90,0:16:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等啊 你是乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.93,0:17:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才重新糊好的拉門 全都給沖爛了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要重新來過了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.70,0:17:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.94,0:17:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 您怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.63,0:17:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉看起來好紅 是不是發燒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 公瑾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.63,0:17:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.58,0:17:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醬油 生薑 胡椒都沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.85,0:17:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去買回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都到了這個時候 還要使喚我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.22,0:17:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.27,0:17:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正常情況下怎麼可能同時沒有醬油生薑胡椒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.89,0:17:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對是在故意刁難我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.63,0:17:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.23,0:17:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.94,0:17:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.23,0:17:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 這個老女人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符 你不想活了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.58,0:18:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.95,0:18:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呂蒙？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.73,0:18:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體不要緊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.03,0:18:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是呂蒙一起來玩就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.36,0:18:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊樂園很有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.05,0:18:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不舒服？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在不想和你說話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.02,0:18:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想說話…發生了什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.39,0:18:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.69,0:19:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量…使用過度了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.22,0:19:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 那個中年婦女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.97,0:19:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 剛才讓我出來買什麼東西來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.02,0:19:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.57,0:19:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.76,0:19:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.38,0:20:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 接下來只等伯符回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.68,0:20:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.60,0:20:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 還真快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.99,0:20:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊 我去拿水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.71,0:20:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.82,0:20:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.38,0:20:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.72,0:20:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼重要的事情你倒是早點說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.26,0:20:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我覺得應該先讓她躺下…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.71,0:20:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.51,0:20:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.79,0:20:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就這麼討厭幹活 竟然不惜編出這種謊話？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:20:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.73,0:21:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.49,0:21:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狡辯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 相信我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.12,0:23:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.52,0:23:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以講講您和過世的父親最初相識的情景嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.26,0:23:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 那是寒冬中的一夜 年方17歲的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.86,0:23:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在被粗暴的鬥士們襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.44,0:23:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人英姿颯爽地出現 並救下我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.20,0:23:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他那時的英姿 直到現在我還歷歷在目難以忘懷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.49,0:23:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 你現在不也是17歲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.55,0:23:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 伯符 你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.98,0:23:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第八話 致人而不致於人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.98,0:23:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs25}出自《孫子兵法》：凡先處戰地而待敵者佚，後處戰地而趨戰者勞。 故善戰者，人而不致於人。
